data.description: Motivated seller .. No City Taxes and No HOA. Come enjoy this 3-acre property, convenient to Weatherford Lake and downtown. Circular drive with large shade trees and a welcoming covered front porch, perfect for lazy afternoons or sipping your morning coffee. Updates give a fresh modern look, painted brick, cedar posts, and a unique roof combination of metal and composition. Step inside to a flexible floorplan with 3 living areas. Updated laminate flooring throughout the downstairs for durability and low maintenance. The main living area features a vaulted ceiling and fireplace with insert, creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings and relaxation. Up the spiral staircase you will find a huge loft overlooking the downstairs.  Sliding glass doors that lead to a large covered back porch. Fenced with a dog kennel in outbuilding provides space for your animals to roam.  Cross fenced, offering ample space for various uses.
